{"text_id":144839,"tokens":["In"," this"," study",","," we"," investigate"," the"," efficiency"," and"," accuracy"," of"," split","-","valence"," Gaussian"," basis"," sets"," in"," conjunction"," with"," the"," heter","ole","vel"," approximation"," for"," the"," computational"," modeling"," of"," peptides"," in"," both"," Restricted"," Hart","ree","-","Fo","ck"," (","R","HF",")"," and"," M\u00f8","ller","-","P","les","set"," second","-","order"," perturbation"," theory"," (","MP","2",")"," methods","."," The"," motivation"," behind"," this"," research"," is"," the"," need"," for"," computationally"," efficient"," and"," reliable"," methods"," to"," predict"," the"," structural"," and"," electronic"," properties"," of"," peptides",","," which"," are"," important"," in"," various"," fields"," such"," as"," drug"," design"," and"," protein"," folding",".","\n\n","Our"," results"," demonstrate"," that"," the"," heter","ole","vel"," approximation",","," which"," allows"," for"," the"," use"," of"," different"," basis"," sets"," for"," different"," atoms"," within"," a"," molecule",","," significantly"," reduces"," the"," computational"," cost"," while"," maintaining"," good"," accuracy"," in"," both"," R","HF"," and"," MP","2"," methods","."," We"," found"," that"," the"," ","6","-","3","1","G","(","d",")"," basis"," set",","," when"," used"," in"," conjunction"," with"," the"," heter","ole","vel"," approximation",","," provides"," a"," good"," balance"," between"," computational"," cost"," and"," accuracy"," for"," peptide"," modeling","."," Furthermore",","," the"," MP","2","/","6","-","3","1","G","(","d",")"," method"," shows"," improved"," performance"," compared"," to"," R","HF","/","6","-","3","1","G","(","d",")"," in"," predicting"," energies"," and"," geometries"," of"," peptide"," systems",".","\n\n","The"," key"," methodology"," of"," this"," work"," is"," the"," combination"," of"," split","-","valence"," Gaussian"," basis"," sets"," and"," the"," heter","ole","vel"," approximation",","," applied"," to"," both"," R","HF"," and"," MP","2"," methods","."," This"," allows"," for"," the"," efficient"," evaluation"," of"," electron"," correlation"," effects",","," which"," are"," critical"," for"," accurately"," modeling"," the"," electronic"," structure"," of"," peptides","."," We"," believe"," that"," the"," findings"," of"," this"," study"," will"," be"," beneficial"," for"," researchers"," in"," the"," fields"," of"," computational"," chemistry"," and"," molecular"," biology",","," as"," they"," provide"," a"," computationally"," efficient"," and"," reliable"," method"," for"," the"," modeling"," of"," peptides","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"mixtral-8x7b","label":1}